message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed and crafted to meet your needs. With its unique features and exceptional quality, it's truly a one-of-a-kind offering. Given its value and benefits, I'm extending this opportunity to you at an exclusive price of $7500. This is an excellent chance to acquire a product that could potentially be worth much more in the future. I look forward to your consideration.
